'''Tacka''' '''n udayen''' neɣ '''tasinagugt''' neɣ '''lkanis''' d adeg i deg ttẓallan [[Tudayt|wudayen]] Aẓar n tecka-agi , anamek-is d adeg ideg ttemlilin lmumnin akken ad ẓẓallen ɣer uɛelṭar n ufakan iqeddsen ; ɣer yimceyyɛen d yinelmaden-nsen . Tasinagugt am wadeg iiqeddsen ɣer wudayen tuɣal akkaseg lexdayem n Ɛezra . Syin syin trennu deg wazal armi tuɣal d taḍrist tudayt n [[Tamezdayt (Asɣan)|tmezdayt]] [[tamasiḥit]]

Ifakanen sɛan adeg iqeddsen ,tazqa n tẓallit , tesɛa idlisen n Turah , tezmer daɣen ad tesɛu taxxamt i umeslay ɣef tmetti . tseɛu daɣen tixxamin meẓẓiyit i ulmud : xas akken tacka n udayen tella d adeg n tẓallit di tazzwara , maca yuɣal deg umezruy uday d adeg n telmud d turah , anamek-is sse"lmaden deg-s ansayen d tutlayt taɛibrit , ama i wid meqqren ama i yilmeẓyen . Iban-d wannecta ɣer Filu askendri , ɣer wudayen n Beniz d udayen n tmura tibelqaniyin , i yettmeslayen s tutlayt tayidicit , semman i yfakanen didaskalya neɣ Skula neɣ Udi anamek-is aɣerbaz . Mazal ismawen agi id-yemmalen afakn qqarenten wid yettmeslayen taydicit . 

Filu askendri d lɛahed amaynut ssexdamayen awal agrigi aqbur προσευχή id-yemmalen taẓallit syin adeg n tẓallit .
